#. Tag: title
#: compare.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Compare</title>"
msgstr "<title>Primerjaj</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; contains several compare functions: <guimenuitem>Compare by "
"Content</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Compare Folders</guimenuitem> and the "
"<link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronizer</link> compare function."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; vsebuje več funkcij za primerjavo: <guimenuitem>Primerjava po "
"vsebini</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Primerjava map</guimenuitem> in "
"primerjalno funkcijo <link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Sinhronizator</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: compare.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compare by Content"
msgstr "Primerjaj po vsebini"

#. Tag: primary
#: compare.docbook:17 compare.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Compare</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Primerjaj</primary>"

#. Tag: secondary
#: compare.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "Content"
msgstr "Vsebina"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select one file in each panel and use <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Compare by content...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. &krusader; "
"will open an external graphical difference tool that is <link linkend="
"\"konfig-dependencies\">configured</link>. &kompare;, <ulink url=\"https://"
"www.kde.org/applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application>KDiff3</"
"application></ulink> and <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/"
"\"><application>xxdiff</application></ulink> are supported."
msgstr ""
"V vsaki plošči izberite eno datoteko in uporabite <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Primerjaj po vsebini ...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. &krusader; bo odprlo zunanje grafično orodje za "
"razliko, ki je <link linkend=\"konfig-dependencies\">konfigurirano</link>. "
"&kompare;, <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/development/kdiff3/"
"\"><application>KDiff3</application></ulink> in <ulink url=\"http://furius. "
"ca/xxdiff/\"><application>xxdiff</application></ulink> so podprti."

#. Tag: title
#: compare.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compare Folders"
msgstr "Primerjaj mape"

#. Tag: secondary
#: compare.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders"
msgstr "Mape"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compare the files of each panel by using <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare Folders</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. By "
"default newer and single files will be selected in each panel, this "
"behaviour can be changed in the <guimenuitem>Compare Setup</guimenuitem> "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"Primerjajte datoteke vsake plošče z uporabo <menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Primerjaj mape</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Privzeto "
"bodo na vsaki plošči izbrane novejše in posamezne datoteke, to vedenje lahko "
"spremenite v meniju <guimenuitem>Primerjaj nastavitve</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The files are not compared by content but by their names and dates only."
msgstr "Datoteke se ne primerjajo po vsebini, temveč le po imenih in datumih."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: compare.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare Setup</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Primerjaj nastavitev</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configures the <guimenuitem>Compare Folders</guimenuitem> function."
msgstr "Konfigurira funkcijo <guimenuitem>Primerjaj mape</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Select Newer and Single</guimenuitem> (default)"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Izberite novejše in enojno</guimenuitem> (privzeto)"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: compare.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Single"
msgstr "Izberite Enotne"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: compare.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Newer"
msgstr "Izberite Novejše"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: compare.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Different and Single"
msgstr "Izberite Različni in Enotni"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: compare.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Different"
msgstr "Izberi drugo"
